core":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:45:20.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"ee62cc2fb85ebc92830cb1fccd87ced33de5a036","tid":605213,"uid":136907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:45:20.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"ee1e6942e8a818654de65d9d77fdda20d09a049e","tid":605213,"uid":136907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"bd9620f5e40116a2a8a05ca65d47895bb4828cdd","tid":605213,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:45:39.000Z","msg":"逝去感情如何留得住......陷家呀剷！"},{"pid":"8b817e627a2c9243880e9c862df29621b8d28bb6","tid":605213,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:45:43.000Z","msg":"攰"},{"pid":"7a07c7760fedf8c82987cd3a990a2a4467331903","tid":605213,"uid":136907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:45:44.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"88b03cf8ae7ce6dc39105c174b16eadc44c2acdb","tid":605213,"uid":105715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:46:37.000Z","msg":"賓周"},{"pid":"8fe3a0a819f207d7b69631f3ff1c33e2a395d803","tid":605213,"uid":21315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:47:16.000Z","msg":"Deadline fighter"},{"pid":"c592b657da116091887b4e0736cff049cdeab48f","tid":605213,"uid":59240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:48:26.000Z","msg":"一笑置之"},{"pid":"6a50edef2333e651b3d824339513074ad00c2539","tid":605213,"uid":177841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:51:42.000Z","msg":"性感泳衣"},{"pid":"9051b2b65f5bd9f1d49f03916bcbf9d0742e5084","tid":605213,"uid":140234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:56:20.000Z","msg":"我有一個朋友<br />\n佢經歷過我人生所有既事情<br />\n我偶然會向其他人提起佢<br />\n但冇人認識佢"},{"pid":"3f42e8cd16de6fc733a2f6f99962ce8364f7fe9f","tid":605213,"uid":136907,"like":12,"dislike":5,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T12:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賓周</blockquote><br />\n賓周：「我從來冇期待過自己可以有咩幸福，有咩成就。就算我幾努力都好，佢根本唔會留意我。我唯一可以做既就係用盡力衝破個圍欄，搵自己既幸福，係我就快衝上去既時候，一下就俾人禁低。但係依個社會到底有幾多條賓周可以揾到幸福，我唔知，我淨係知我只可以一世望住個撻黃跡。"},{"pid":"2cf0325a5bde1abf4ddabd2a07f7c03723bb5cf5","tid":605213,"uid":136907,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:07:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Deadline fighter</blockquote><br />\n我曾經問自己點解要做一個deadine fighter，係我太懶，定係我冇留意。可能每一個人係感情上都做過，有d人肥咗，有d人反而高分。但係今次我唔合格。我失去左你。"},{"pid":"e3ea5c7511e70102ee14b69f711113a9654f9733","tid":605213,"uid":50779,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:11:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"546b770fdea20315c694e0e8a33862d593fc9d33","tid":605213,"uid":136907,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T13:49:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>攰</blockquote><br />\n嗰日瞓醒，我竟然見到床邊有著住碎花裙嘅鹿仔送早餐我食。<br />\n我從來都唔信呢個世界有咁荒謬嘅事。<br />\n所以我拒絕咗佢：「唔洗喇唔該，請問我喺邊？」<br />\n我都唔知點解我會咁問，不過覺得實在好奇怪<br />\n花鹿佢冇答我，我留意佢嘅笑容由微笑轉變為咧嘴冷笑，嘅身體開始扭曲澎脹變大。<br />\n轉眼間，只見一隻滿身血肉嘅怪物張住血口向我大叫。<br />\n驚恐間我從惡夢中醒來，<br />\n回到現實的我，知道另一個惡夢才正式開始，<br />\n<br />\n我攰了。"},{"pid":"90571b88b9e472e366505d23197cdb213582500e","tid":605213,"uid":136907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T14:01:16.000Z","msg":"忽發奇想一段<br />\n<br />\n每年同一樣嘅時間同一樣嘅地點，都有一個唔識嘅人幫我斟酒，然後俾一支煙我。明明同佢講我想要水唔要酒，但係佢點左三下頭，然後就轉身走。即使係咁，我每年同一樣嘅時間同一樣嘅地點都會番黎依到。"},{"pid":"49bf39b9653877e1a37f2fbad962d1ade238dbab","tid":605213,"uid":98698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T14:04:27.000Z","msg":"異地"},{"pid":"e21e0d72f562cae55ef3d6907d2291e5bc8539b0","tid":605213,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T14:10:51.000Z","msg":"前後"},{"pid":"5c9f4a377112f821d916c8ddb8bddd8a70ceaa75","tid":605213,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"長頸鹿"},{"pid":"87534d30251b731a706214f970b5bb1433083529","tid":605213,"uid":171789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T14:52:50.000Z","msg":"自卑"},{"pid":"c74bde023b148c39c1aa916b9b72a65790a5b20c","tid":605213,"uid":152262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:01:18.000Z","msg":"黎耀輝"},{"pid":"1bed2bf265f609c5c3684b56a2ba65c0afcfa69d","tid":605213,"uid":160378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:03:21.000Z","msg":"重頭嚟過"},{"pid":"3eae00b45b7e5ffc81fe4b88d2d0105a081ddae3","tid":605213,"uid":47752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:04:52.000Z","msg":"絕望"},{"pid":"0ce9cfc286965dba511501397b83c8c99188c3e4","tid":605213,"uid":78522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:06:04.000Z","msg":"FC鬥"},{"pid":"9154f951815265d5b700acd1ca5a056342c4d3fe","tid":605213,"uid":166368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:10:34.000Z","msg":"心痛"},{"pid":"fb3f201832d32aa00947079e8095b731689d0ef6","tid":605213,"uid":46151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"90571b88b9e472e366505d23197cdb213582500e","tid":605213,"uid":136907,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T14:01:16.000Z","msg":"忽發奇想一段<br />\n<br />\n每年同一樣嘅時間同一樣嘅地點，都有一個唔識嘅人幫我斟酒，然後俾一支煙我。明明同佢講我想要水唔要酒，但係佢點左三下頭，然後就轉身走。即使係咁，我每年同一樣嘅時間同一樣嘅地點都會番黎依到。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:13:49.000Z","msg":"煙點會淨係點一支"},{"pid":"340fae5b4f4e03018c8ca34393ca95a5b8d067c6","tid":605213,"uid":30830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:23:51.000Z","msg":"肛交"},{"pid":"815043492a2ac152273e9e4a9b0ad74232d2f205","tid":605213,"uid":177154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"癲狗症"},{"pid":"3ba576aee65c374b506beae3293158d0d2ea1295","tid":605213,"uid":144789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T19:13:01.000Z","msg":"阡陌"},{"pid":"dd57d58cf3621fefcac181ece3979b03a9ce7ba6","tid":605213,"uid":117677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T19:14:43.000Z","msg":"無奈"},{"pid":"000bd45d688f3c484c6020c36e567befa47155e9","tid":605213,"uid":153395,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T19:16:44.000Z","msg":"後備之中再後備的觀音兵"},{"pid":"ac4b081f0d048619901d1dbed65f38f995bd3617","tid":605213,"uid":96732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T19:33:39.000Z","msg":"時間"},{"pid":"6a64690d0f863eeaaf1f2a37094ac63c8eff9350","tid":605213,"uid":53970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T19:38:24.000Z","msg":"阿木"},{"pid":"319d02e2c273e27922ea0eabb5e9eac2deba02af","tid":605213,"uid":72321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a64690d0f863eeaaf1f2a37094ac63c8eff9350","tid":605213,"uid":53970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T19:38:24.000Z","msg":"阿木"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"不如你唔好叫阿木？"},{"pid":"bdd8e085320569ca7838e127778d150b4485ddb8","tid":605213,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"319d02e2c273e27922ea0eabb5e9eac2deba02af","tid":605213,"uid":72321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6a64690d0f863eeaaf1f2a37094ac63c8eff9350","tid":605213,"uid":53970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T19:38:24.000Z","msg":"阿木"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T05:44:28.000Z","msg":"不如你唔好叫阿木？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T05:55:22.000Z","msg":"索性叫條廢柴啦你"},{"pid":"85871caefafd2ab88b2e85663248510cf0353707","tid":605213,"uid":95759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"放棄治療"},{"pid":"8b2d1914af99bcd298e16d66851bd340d8592f5d","tid":605213,"uid":9450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T06:25:14.000Z","msg":"想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"334f93ac50488ad96e6aa45af707cee89842cd85","tid":605213,"uid":136907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T07:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一笑置之</blockquote><br />\n曾經參加過反普教中遊行既我，有一日有個小學生走黎問我：「老師我有問題問你。」我雛眉，叫佢講翻廣東話。有一日學校請左個內地官員黎參觀，然後佢問我：「老師我有問題問你。」<br />\n「是的，請問什麼事情？」"},{"pid":"cc43a03d730f67d7e319e807934b5893db5d9a22","tid":605213,"uid":136907,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>性感泳衣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我好想著起你，但係我唔敢，掛左你係衣架已經有三年。望住ig上既女仔個個著起都好靚，我都係女仔黎嫁，只係身體上唔同。"},{"pid":"c173beac33178084109a573bda4e47e470475b75","tid":605213,"uid":153015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc43a03d730f67d7e319e807934b5893db5d9a22","tid":605213,"uid":136907,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T08:12:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>性感泳衣</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我好想著起你，但係我唔敢，掛左你係衣架已經有三年。望住ig上既女仔個個著起都好靚，我都係女仔黎嫁，只係身體上唔同。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T08:18:13.000Z","msg":"呢段好"},{"pid":"6ecb01d85ae2265f3b6abcdda33cbaafc7b2b07e","tid":605213,"uid":144718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T08:21:44.000Z","msg":"牛肺"}]}